content:
I didn't think about that. Let me think for a sec... *rummages through fridge and pantry* Oh, yeah! I remember now! I also got some carrots, onions, and potatoes, which I was planning to use for a stew or something. And I think I got a can of black beans and some diced tomatoes too. Hmm, maybe I can use those for a bean soup or something.

You know, it's funny. I was just about to throw away the receipt from last Saturday, but I'm glad I didn't. *pulls out receipt* Let me take a look... *scans receipt* Oh, yeah! I also got some ground beef, which I was planning to use for tacos or something. And I got some frozen peas and corn too. Okay, I think that's everything.

Thanks for reminding me to check my fridge and pantry! I feel like I've got a better idea of what I've got to work with now.
